{"tid":1336043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［香城App 2.0］聽朝要買裝嘅全部同我入嚟！！","createTime":"2019-07-20T18:22:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T03:48:15.000Z","uid":33736,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"07d1e276fea837983b367fd2285b0a6c5a108e36","tid":1336043,"uid":33736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:22:46.000Z","msg":"hi又係我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知道仲有好多人未買齊裝<br />\n但未齊裝又點玩香城Online 721公測？<br />\n1500正式開Ser，大家仲有一朝早去買嘢<br />\n<br />\n但眼見好多手足都唔知去邊度買嘢好<br />\n於是，香城Online App就加入咗新功能：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">俾大家分享購物好去處嘅地圖！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><a href=\"http://hkonline.glideapp.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkonline.glideapp.io&d=3A6Iqvk0VBPdaidkhJ82WxAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=292a8b7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hkonline.glideapp.io</a></strong><br />\n<br />\nClick入去右邊Shopping Map<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7VwML9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7VwML9a.jpg&h=6591bf11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n㩒右上角加號<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b0AtZt9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb0AtZt9.jpg&h=43b20493&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n填完商店資料（address一欄記得唔好有中文），再㩒右上個tick<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">即可同大家分享邊度有咩買</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n快啲幫我補完購物地圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><a href=\"http://hkonline.glideapp.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkonline.glideapp.io&d=3A6Iqvk0VBPdaidkhJ82WxAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=292a8b7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hkonline.glideapp.io</a></strong>"},{"pid":"2194c5a854228fb260a7e612d03b67dd67a510b4","tid":1336043,"uid":33736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:24:02.000Z","msg":"另外首頁加入咗啲有用嘅link<br />\n同埋Info頁加入咗啲有用嘅資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時間不仿睇睇"},{"pid":"7e90dc63eea113f624b0715fc131f49b0ba06e5b","tid":1336043,"uid":33736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:24:17.000Z","msg":"同我推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c0159ccce568011c7ecc40b08e339ce272c999","tid":1336043,"uid":58093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:24:56.000Z","msg":"唔知灣仔5金開唔開呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1650b96fc55a80219ed2c0b01f8eb18657b2868","tid":1336043,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:25:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cd314048215cb193a424e97704aa5ae1c0f8e440","tid":1336043,"uid":33736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66c0159ccce568011c7ecc40b08e339ce272c999","tid":1336043,"uid":58093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:24:56.000Z","msg":"唔知灣仔5金開唔開呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:26:22.000Z","msg":"出新填地or ssp啦"},{"pid":"b86a61a49083f572d7c15fabe8695a03f125efd3","tid":1336043,"uid":100321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:27:22.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"96794192ad77b5eceb35916bcb9cd0d1b34c77c1","tid":1336043,"uid":51467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:28:22.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"50cdac260b72567db1c5c8dd5d639f94f3ea0aaa","tid":13